<h1>Share-Backed Financing &amp; Equity-Backed Funding Asia | Squadron Capital</h1>
<p>&nbsp;Squadron Capital is a leading provider of alternative financing solutions, specializing in private credit and equity-backed funding across the Asia-Pacific region. With more than 15 years of operational experience in Asia, the firm has built a strong reputation for providing direct capital to listed companies, major shareholders, and high-net-worth individuals (HNWIs). Its financing solutions include share-backed financing, equity-backed funding, margin financing, wealth management, corporate finance, capital allocation, private banking, private credit, pre-IPO funding, reverse mergers, block trades, and private placements. The company serves clients across Hong Kong, Singapore, Thailand, Malaysia, Japan, Australia, Indonesia, the Philippines, Vietnam, Taiwan, Canada, Europe, Mexico, South America, the Middle East, Turkey, and the United Kingdom.</p>
