<p>&nbsp;Squadron Capital maintains deep expertise across Asia-Pacific's primary financial centers. Its core markets include Hong Kong, Singapore, Japan, Thailand, Australia, Malaysia, Indonesia, the Philippines, Vietnam, and Taiwan, while also supporting clients in additional international markets such as Canada, Europe, Turkey, Mexico, South America, the Middle East, and the United Kingdom. This broad regional presence enables the company to structure cross-border financing solutions tailored to the specific regulatory and market requirements of each jurisdiction.</p>
<p>&nbsp;The firm's service portfolio extends beyond equity-backed funding to include block trades, cross-border transaction structuring, innovation partnerships, and EB-5 investment immigration solutions. By combining institutional-grade execution with strict confidentiality, Squadron Capital provides sophisticated financing options designed to meet the needs of listed companies, significant shareholders, family offices, private bankers, and ultra-high-net-worth individuals seeking flexible access to capital across international markets.</p>
<p>&nbsp;Headquartered at Marina Bay Financial Centre Tower 2 in Singapore, Squadron Capital serves clients through its regional offices and multilingual capabilities, supporting various local markets in multiple languages. The company continues to focus on delivering transparent, confidential, and efficient capital solutions while helping clients unlock liquidity from listed equity holdings through professionally structured financing arrangements.</p>
